name: LaFaye GASKINS, Petitioner v. Peter F. ROGERS, Judge, Court of Common Pleas Philadelphia, Respondent

parties: LaFaye GASKINS, Petitioner v. Peter F. ROGERS, Judge, Court of Common Pleas Philadelphia, Respondent.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 13th day of February, 2012, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Mandamus and/or Extraordinary Relief is DENIED. The Prothonotary is directed to strike the jurist’s name from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
